title.narrative: Reducing Technical Barriers for Entrepreneurship and Trade

description.narrative: The overall project development objective is to streamline the compulsory standards requirements for business, develop systems to enhance product quality and safety, and increase enterprise competitiveness in pilot sectors. The key project outcomes will be a decrease in the cost of regulatory compliance for business and, in the longer term, an increase in the share of non-gold trade with WTO partners.
